{
  "stem": "15393.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] One of the Gestapo men wanted to take the boy aside and tell him to go, but he didn't want to leave.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He didn't want to.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Wanted to stay with the father.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that was that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Now-- [DRINKS] the 15th of August 1942 is when my father and my brother, as far as we're concerned, died.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Died by whose hand, by what means, we shall never know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "From that moment on when we stayed behind, I need not go into-- needn't tell you how broken my mother was to lose a husband and a child in one day.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And so she had me, but I was no substitute.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But I was there and she had to fend for me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And in those days although I was young-- I was a child, really, but one was not a child anymore.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "One was very, very what you would call today streetwise, I imagine.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "One was much more than streetwise.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "One was certainly-- when I think of things today, I don't think I could do today what I could do then being aged 10, 11, 12, 13.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Wouldn't occur to me that it might be possible, but one did then.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And so my mother and I went to our grandparents and stayed with them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And then we had to slowly move into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They were now moving everybody into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And the ghetto was not closed up yet completely.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "It was, in other words, what they called an open ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "That meant that people could go out to work out of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Because there was no work in the ghetto they had-- all the labor force was from the ghetto to the outside, to the other side.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So it was open.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
